            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">How to Import Your Firearm Data from a Spreadsheet</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">Already tracking your collection in Excel or Google Sheets? Here's how to bring that data into Arsenal Vault without retyping everything.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3 mr-1"></i> March 29, 2026</span>
                <span><i class="bi bi-clock mr-1"></i> 6 min read</span>
            </div>
